---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const wppLink = "https://wa.me/5531997289558?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20gostaria%20de%20uma%20consultoria%20gratuita!";
// Coloque o link do Instagram da loja abaixo
const instaLink = "https://www.instagram.com/cas4itabirito/"; 

// Link oficial da sua loja no Google Maps
const mapsLink = "https://maps.google.com/?cid=15422740762560078729&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQ"; 
---

<footer class="bg-[#051830] pt-20 pb-10 border-t-4 border-[#B28D42] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-32 -mr-32 w-96 h-96 bg-[#B28D42] opacity-[0.03] rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-16">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-5">
        <img 
          src="/logo-branca.png" 
          alt="Cas4 Pisos & Ambientes" 
          class="w-40 md:w-48 h-auto object-contain mb-6" 
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-sm text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-md">
          A loja especialista em pisos vinílicos e laminados. Também trabalhamos com persianas, porcelanatos, pisos cerâmicos, louças e metais. Unimos sofisticação, conforto e foco na melhor solução para o seu ambiente em Itabirito e região.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <a href={instaLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-[#B28D42] hover:text-[#051830] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href={wppLink} id="icone-tel-footer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-[#B28D42] hover:text-[#051830] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm" aria-label="WhatsApp">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" id="icone-tel-footer" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-3">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#B28D42]"></span>
          Navegação Rápida
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li><a href="#diferenciais" class="hover:text-[#B28D42] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><span class="text-[#B28D42] opacity-0 -ml-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all duration-300">→</span> Por que a Cas4?</a></li>
          <li><a href="#produtos" class="hover:text-[#B28D42] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><span class="text-[#B28D42] opacity-0 -ml-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all duration-300">→</span> Nossas Linhas</a></li>
          <li><a href="#portfolio" class="hover:text-[#B28D42] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><span class="text-[#B28D42] opacity-0 -ml-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all duration-300">→</span> Portfólio</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq" class="hover:text-[#B28D42] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"><span class="text-[#B28D42] opacity-0 -ml-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-0 transition-all duration-300">→</span> Dúvidas Frequentes</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-4">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#B28D42]"></span>
          Contato & Localização
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-6 text-sm text-slate-300">
          
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#B28D42] flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-white mb-1 font-medium tracking-wide">Showroom Itabirito</strong>
              <a href={mapsLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block leading-relaxed text-slate-400 hover:text-[#B28D42] transition-colors group">
                R. Raul Soares, 186 - Centro<br/>
                Itabirito - MG, 35450-003
                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-[#B28D42] mt-1.5 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity uppercase tracking-wider">
                  Abrir rota no mapa 
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17l9.2-9.2M17 17V7H7"/></svg>
                </span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#B28D42] flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-white mb-1 font-medium tracking-wide">Atendimento Especializado</strong>
              <a href={wppLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block hover:text-[#B28D42] text-slate-400 transition-colors">(31) 9 9728-9558</a>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#B28D42] flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="block text-white mb-1 font-medium tracking-wide">Horários de Funcionamento</strong>
              <span class="leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Segunda a Sexta: 08:30 às 18:00<br/>Sábados: 08:00 às 12:00</span>
            </div>
          </li>

        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500 gap-4 md:gap-0">
      <p>&copy; {year} Cas4 Pisos & Ambientes. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</footer>